01:04:58,120 --> 01:05:02,011
Of the gifts we'll receive

904
01:05:02,120 --> 01:05:05,841
As long as there's Christmas

905
01:05:05,960 --> 01:05:09,851
We'll all be just fine

906
01:05:09,960 --> 01:05:13,760
A star shines above us

907
01:05:13,880 --> 01:05:15,769
Lighting your way

908
01:05:15,880 --> 01:05:19,043
And mine

909
01:05:26,280 --> 01:05:28,169
Light my way

910
01:05:28,280 --> 01:05:30,886
You know I will

911
01:05:33,560 --> 01:05:37,565
As long as there's Christmas

912
01:05:37,680 --> 01:05:41,526
I truly believe

913
01:05:41,640 --> 01:05:45,531
That hope is the greatest

914
01:05:45,640 --> 01:05:49,486
Of the gifts we'll receive

915
01:05:49,600 --> 01:05:54,083
As long as our guiding star

916
01:05:54,200 --> 01:05:57,443
Shines above

917
01:05:57,560 --> 01:06:01,690
There'll always be Christmas

918
01:06:03,160 --> 01:06:07,245
So there always
will be a time

919
01:06:07,360 --> 01:06:11,410
When the world
is filled with peace

920
01:06:11,520 --> 01:06:14,763
And love

